_:N1e77ef73f76c4f8aa7d65c0d047605d7 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Bridget Phillipson was appointed Secretary of State for Education on 5 July 2024 and Minister for Women and Equalities on 8 July 2024.</p>\n\n<p>She was elected as the Labour MP for Houghton and Sunderland South in May 2010.</p>\n" .
